features: Locked edge design. The edges of our kitchen mats are designed with machine-locked edges, which ensures that the edges are flat (to prevent tripping over the edges) and will not fall apart after machine cleaning.

Rolled ring design (durable). The roller ring design combined with polypropylene creates a three-dimensional effect, and the high-quality, anti-fatigue mat material will not disintegrate or compress over time. Therefore, your continuous use will not compromise any of its value. What's more, thanks to its soft and tough surface, you don't have to worry about your pet's claws or sharp objects damaging the surface of the mat and your floor, reducing your excess expenses.

High stain resistance. The mat is made of 100% polypropylene, which helps prevent oily water from leaving unsightly stains on your floor while cooking. Best of all, the back of this kitchen rug will not melt on your floor and damage it.

Washable non-slip kitchen carpet and pad: The back of the kitchen carpet is made of a rubber material with a twill grid and rubber backing for maximum protection against shifting or slipping, ensuring safety, fade resistance and abrasion resistance. [Note] Only place the mat on a dry, flat surface and always keep the bottom of the rug dry. Water under the carpet may cause slipping.

Note: Our carpets are delivered to you rolled up and packaged. After you receive the mat, open the reverse roll and unroll it, and it will work fine. If you have any other problems, please do not hesitate to contact us and we will provide the best solution for you as soon as possible.
